data.description: Affordable Eastside Location! Check out this cute bungalow on Terre Haute's eastside. Looking for that first home, this might be the one for you. This 2 bedroom 1 bath home features hardwood flooring, good size rooms and a dining/kitchen combo with extra room for storage or for the laundry to be relocated to. Out back you'll find a fenced yard perfect for the kids or dogs to play.
